<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
    android:id="@+id/scrollView"
    android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
    android:layout_centerHorizontal="true">
    <RelativeLayout
        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
        android:paddingRight="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
        android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        tools:context="com.bvmiste.vision16.Eventactivity.civil1"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content">

        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
            android:id="@+id/id1">

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:gravity="center"
                android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceLarge"
                android:text="Silicon Valley"
                android:textColor="@color/primary"
                android:id="@+id/textView1" />

        </LinearLayout>

        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
            android:id="@+id/id2"
            android:layout_below="@+id/id1">

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceLarge"
                android:text="
Round -1:  Inquizive

Quiz (Aptitude questions, True/False, General Knowledge, Crossword, Answer in 1 or 2 words)

Round2: Group Discussion

It would be conducted on the next day of 1st round. Selected participants will be divided into 2
groups for group discussion. They will be judged by our professors.
Topic will be given after the formation of groups.
Marking: The answer should contain proper fact. Only English language is to be used. Formal outfit is
compulsory.

Round 3: Blogatica(surprise)

A topic will given on which they have to make blog using word press or Google blog or any tools and
winners would be selected on the basis of blog content and presentation they give about their blog
in front of jury."
                android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                android:id="@+id/textView2" />
        </LinearLayout>

        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="horizontal"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
            android:layout_below="@+id/id2">


            <TextView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center"
                android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceLarge"
                android:text="Event Leader: Ria Chaudhari.
Mobile no.: 8128943481"
                android:textColor="@color/colorAccent"
                android:id="@+id/textView3" />


        </LinearLayout>

    </RelativeLayout>

</ScrollView>
